data.description: Welcome to your new home in beautiful Spring Valley Lake! Your new home has an open floor plan with vinyl dual pane windows, window shutters, tile floors and plush carpet and recessed lighting. The kitchen was recently beautifully upgraded with granite counters and new cabinets, has a large walk-in pantry and stainless steel appliances. There is a brick fireplace that offers a touch of charm to cozy up to on cold winter nights. Both bathrooms have been updated, there are ceiling fans in all bedrooms and the master bedroom has a walk-in closet. All this in a quiet neighborhood with amenities including a 200 acre lake with boating, marina and fuel, fishing areas, a beach with swimming area, a club house, golfing, 3 parks, one with redesigned running & exercise stations, kayaking, paddleboarding, jet skiing, baseball & dog park, horse equestrian area as well as 24-hour patrolled security throughout the community. This is a great opportunity for families, professionals and investors who want the feel of quiet living near the lake and close to shopping, restaurants, parks and schools.
